# StegoVault

## Secure Image Steganography Platform

StegoVault is a modern web-based steganography application that enables users to securely hide and extract secret messages inside digital images using multiple Least Significant Bit (LSB) embedding techniques.

The platform provides a user-friendly interface for encoding confidential text into images and decoding hidden messages from stego-images. It supports several steganographic profiles, channel-based embedding methods, and optional password-based XOR encryption for enhanced security.

---

## Features

### Message Encoding

* Hide secret text inside image files.
* Generate stego-images without visible image distortion.
* Support for multiple steganographic algorithms.

### Message Decoding

* Extract hidden messages from stego-images.
* Recover encrypted messages using the correct password.
* Validate profile-based extraction methods.

### Security Profiles

| Key ID | Method           | Description                                        |
| ------ | ---------------- | -------------------------------------------------- |
| K1     | LSB-1 Classic    | Standard 1-bit LSB embedding                       |
| K2     | LSB-2 Dual Bit   | Uses 2 LSBs per channel for higher capacity        |
| K3     | LSB-4 Quad Bit   | Uses 4 LSBs per channel for maximum payload        |
| K4     | Red Channel      | Embeds data only in the Red channel                |
| K5     | Green Channel    | Embeds data only in the Green channel              |
| K6     | Blue Channel     | Embeds data only in the Blue channel               |
| K7     | Alpha Channel    | Embeds data in transparency information            |
| K8     | XOR Cipher + LSB | Password-protected XOR encryption before embedding |

### Modern User Interface

* Responsive React frontend.
* Real-time image preview.
* Simple drag-and-drop image upload workflow.
* Dark-themed cybersecurity-inspired design.

