## API Endpoints

### Health Check

```http
GET /api/stego/health
```

Response:

```json
{
  "status": "online",
  "module": "StegoVault Processing Core Engine"
}
```

---

### Encode Message

```http
POST /api/stego/encode
```

Form Data:

```text
image
message
keyId
password
```

Returns:

```text
Encoded PNG image
```

---

### Decode Message

```http
POST /api/stego/decode
```

Form Data:

```text
image
keyId
password
```

Response:

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Hidden Secret Message"
}
```

